org.ow2.chameleon.metric
Class DerivedUnitBuilder<Q extends Quantity<Q>>

java.lang.Object
  org.ow2.chameleon.metric.DerivedUnitBuilder<Q>

public class DerivedUnitBuilder<Q extends Quantity<Q>>
extends Object

Builder to create derived units. This class can also be used to create base units, but its now its primary purpose. final Unit newton = new DerivedUnitBuilder().from(GRAM).times(SI.METRE) .pow(SI.SECOND, -2).name("newton").symbol("N").build();
